NAME

    Catmandu::Fix::File - Catmandu fixes to check file attributes

SYNOPSIS

      use Catmandu::Fix::File;
    
      # all fix functions are exported by default

DESCRIPTION

    Catmandu::Fix::File includes the following Catmandu::Fix functions:

      * Catmandu::Fix::basename

      * Catmandu::Fix::dirname

      * Catmandu::Fix::file_size

      * Catmandu::Fix::human_byte_size

      * Catmandu::Fix::Condition::file_test

